<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.1">
<l>puḷḷā yēṉamumāyp pukunteṉṉai yuḷḷaṅkoṇṭa</l>
<l>kaḷvā veṉṟalumeṉ kaṇkaṇīrkaḷ cōrtarumāl</l>
<l>uḷḷē niṉṟuruki neñcamuṉṉai yuḷḷiyakkāl</l>
<l>naḷḷē ṉuṉṉaiyallāl naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As soon as [I] say, ‘Rogue who, entering me, captured my heart,</l>
<l>As a bird and a boar,’ my eyes will naturally let flow tears, for sure;</l>
<l>At the time that my heart thinks of you, melting from within,</l>
<l>I do not love [any] but you, O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
